headline: Delta is beefing up its in-flight menu with Shake Shack burgers
summary: Delta Air Lines (DAL) is about to start serving a tasty new item on its first-class menu. The company announced Tuesday that premium flyers will soon be able to chow down on Shake Shack burgers mid-air.
